---
const faqs = [
  {
    q: "Is this really free?",
    a: "Yes. OpenBoil is MIT licensed, completely free and open source. No hidden costs, no premium tiers for the boilerplate itself.",
  },
  {
    q: "Can I use this for commercial projects?",
    a: "Absolutely. The MIT license allows commercial use. Build and sell as many SaaS products as you want.",
  },
  {
    q: "How do I switch providers?",
    a: "Change a single value in openboil.config.ts. For example, switching from Firebase to Supabase auth is literally changing \"firebase\" to \"supabase\".",
  },
  {
    q: "Do I need all the providers set up to run locally?",
    a: "No. Enable Demo Mode from the template switcher to browse all pages with a fake user. You only need real provider credentials when you're ready to go live.",
  },
  {
    q: "What about the AI features? Do they cost money?",
    a: "The AI providers (OpenAI, Anthropic, Google) have their own pricing. OpenBoil includes the integration code and credit system — you bring your own API keys.",
  },
  {
    q: "Can I remove features I don't need?",
    a: "Yes. Set any feature to false in the config (blog, ai, admin, credits) and it's disabled. The code is modular — nothing is tightly coupled.",
  },
];
---

<section class="py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <p class="text-sm font-medium text-primary mb-3">FAQ</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight">
        Common questions
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="divide-y divide-border">
      {faqs.map((faq) => (
        <details class="group py-5">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer list-none">
            <span class="text-sm font-medium pr-8">{faq.q}</span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-muted-foreground flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed pr-12">{faq.a}</p>
        </details>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
